main event: A UFO was tracked on radar at a USAF station in Grandview, Missouri in March 1962.
interesting points: The object appeared directly on the radar scope and could be tracked and followed., It traveled at varying speeds from subsonic to over 600 knots., The object appeared white and extremely bright., It made drastic maneuver changes impossible for conventional aircraft., USAF Lt. J. Allen Hynek analyzed the report and noted it was consistent with known UFO phenomena.
witness description: reported via radar and analyzed by USAF personnel
